title: From Patient To Physician | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: From Patient To Physician | Joel Osteen
description:
God is counting on us to make a difference in the lives of others. When you use what you've been through to bring healing to those around you, there's no limit to what God can do in your life!


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
